		&#x3C;input id=&#x22;radio-option-3&#x22; type=&#x22;radio&#x22; name=&#x22;radio-example&#x22;&#x3E;
		&#x3C;label for=&#x22;radio-option-3&#x22;&#x3E;Option 3&#x3C;/label&#x3E;
	&#x3C;/li&#x3E;
&#x3C;/ul&#x3E;

<p>Note: <code>gc-form</code> can be applied to parent elements other than the unordered list</p></code></pre>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
<section>
	<h2>CSS class configuration options</h2>
	<dl class="dl-horizontal">
		<dt><code>form-label-inline</code></dt>
		<dd>Component: Inline form elements. Apply to each label.</dd>
		<dt><code>checkbox-green</code></dt>
		<dd>Component: Success checkboxes with green background. Apply to each large checkbox list item.</dd>
		<dt><code>checkbox-green-small</code></dt>
		<dd>Component: Success checkboxes with green background. Apply to each small checkbox list item.</dd>
		<dt><code>disabled</code></dt>
		<dd>Component: Disabled state on form controls. Add ".disabled" to the input field and ".is-disabled" to the checkbox or radio button list item.</dd>
	</dl>
</section>
